room_title: Escape room "North Pole Meltdown" by Escape Artist in Charlotte
room_description:
Bert the Elf has informed you that he has seen this years Nice List and your name is not on it.

He has also informed you that Santa will be out if the workshop on a training run with the reindeer which gives you the opportunity to get into Santa's workshop find the Nice List and put your name on it.
